          <p>
            One night i received a call from a close friend. He have had an idea to be able to create a system that allowed the homeless to receive donations in a contact-less society.
            I set myself a challenge to spend one evening and come up with a proof of concept for how this could work.
          </p>
          <p>
            <h3>How it works</h3>
              Each vulnerable person is given a QR code that they could produce to the donator. The donator will then take their mobile from their pocket and without having to download an app or setup an account, scan the QR code and donate a sum of money to the individual.
          </p>
          <p>
            <h3>How to test it</h3>

            <ol>
              <li>To test on mobile, open up your camera app and point it to the QR code above
                To test on desktop, click the button above</li>

              <li>
                Choose your donation amount
              </li>

              <li>
                Donate using apple pay/ google pay by clicking the button and following the instructions on the device<br>
                Donate using a card number by using the following card details:<br>
                Number: 4242424242424242<br>
                CVC: any 3 digits<br>
                Date: any date in the future.<br>
              </li>
            </ol>

              <strong>NOTE: While you will not be charged to test this application, please do not type in your real information.</strong>

          </p>
